perl-glib: perl-glib (Perl interface to GLib)
perl-glib:
perl-glib: This module provides perl access to Glib and GLib's GObject libraries.
perl-glib: GLib is a portability and utility library; GObject provides a generic
perl-glib: type system with inheritance and a powerful signal system. Together
perl-glib: these libraries are used as the foundation for many of the libraries
perl-glib: that make up the Gnome environment, and are used in many unrelated
perl-glib: projects.
perl-glib:
perl-glib: http://search.cpan.org/dist/Glib/
perl-glib: Packager: _PACKAGER on _BUILD_DATE
